description.en: Star Cactus is a small, eye-catching succulent with a distinctive star-shaped body covered in tiny spines. Ideal for indoor display or as part of a succulent collection, it thrives in bright light and requires minimal watering. Its unique shape and compact size make it a charming, low-maintenance plant.
variants.images.label: Star cactus

description.en: Nursery pot is a lightweight, practical container designed to support healthy root growth and provide excellent drainage. Made for growing, transporting, and caring for plants, it focuses on function rather than style. Perfect for keeping your plant healthy until you place it in a decorative pot of your choice.
variants.images.label: Nursery Pot:

description.en: Mammillaria hahniana, also known as the Old Lady Cactus, is a charming, round cactus covered in soft white spines and delicate wool. In bright light, it produces lovely pink flowers that form a crown around the top. Easy to care for and visually striking, it’s a delightful addition to any cactus collection.
variants.images.label: Mammillaria hahniana

description.en: Pilosocereus azureus is a stunning blue cactus with tall, columnar growth and soft, golden spines that create a beautiful contrast against its cool-toned skin. Thriving in bright light and requiring minimal watering, it’s an easy-care plant that brings a unique, sculptural desert charm to any collection.
variants.images.label: Pilosocereus azureus

description.en: Hoya Hearts are charming succulent hearts, usually grown from a single Hoya kerrii leaf. They love bright, indirect light and require very infrequent watering. Small, long-lasting, and incredibly cute, they are perfect for gifts, small spaces, and adding a stylish green accent to any interior.

Fibrestone Trough Pot is a durable, weather-resistant planter designed for outdoor use. Made from lightweight yet sturdy fibrestone, it combines the natural look of stone with easy handling. Ideal for flowers, shrubs, or small trees, it provides excellent drainage and a stylish, modern touch to gardens, patios, or balconies.
variants.images.label: Fibrestone Trough Pot

description.en: Echeveria 'Purple Pearl' is a stunning succulent with large, smooth rosettes in soft shades of purple and pink. It thrives in bright light and requires only occasional watering, making it easy to care for. Its vibrant color and elegant shape add a touch of sophistication to any succulent display or indoor arrangement.
variants.images.label: Echeveria 'Purple Pearl'

description.en: Haworthia limifolia is a striking succulent known for its dark green, ridged leaves arranged in a perfect rosette. Compact and easy to care for, it thrives in bright, indirect light and needs only occasional watering. Its unique texture and geometric form make it an elegant, low-maintenance addition to any plant collection.
variants.images.label: Haworthia limifolia

description.en: Spathiphyllum wallisii, commonly known as the Peace Lily, is a popular indoor plant admired for its glossy green leaves and elegant white blooms. It thrives in low to bright indirect light and prefers moderate watering. Easy to care for, it brings a touch of freshness and tranquility to any indoor space.
variants.images.label: Spathiphyllum wallisii

description.en: Panda Plant is a charming succulent known for its soft, fuzzy leaves edged with chocolate-brown tips. Thriving in bright light and requiring very little water, it’s an easy-care plant with a unique, velvety texture. Its cute, compact form makes it a delightful addition to any succulent collection or indoor display.
variants.images.label: Panda Plant

description.en: Echinocactus grusonii, commonly known as the Golden Barrel Cactus, is a spherical cactus species native to central Mexico. It has a thick, ribbed, globe-shaped body covered with prominent golden-yellow spines and produces small yellow flowers near the crown when mature. It is widely grown as an ornamental plant due to its striking appearance and high tolerance to drought.
variants.images.label: Echinocactus grusonii

description.en: Moth orchid is a graceful, easy-care orchid known for its long-lasting, butterfly-like blooms. It thrives in bright, indirect light and prefers a well-draining medium to keep its roots healthy. With minimal watering and a bit of humidity, it rewards you with elegant flowers for weeks. Your moth orchid will arrive in a nursery pot, ready to be placed in a decorative pot for a stunning display.
variants.images.label: Boquetto Sensation

description.en: Bird of Paradise is a stunning indoor tropical known for its large, bold leaves and exotic, bird-like flowers when mature. It thrives in bright, indirect light and enjoys regular watering with good humidity. With its impressive size and lush, architectural look, it brings a dramatic, tropical vibe to any room.
variants.images.label: Bird of Paradise

description.en: Aeschynanthus japhrolepsis is a beautiful trailing plant known for its glossy green leaves and elegant cascading growth. Thriving in bright, indirect light and enjoying moderate watering, it’s easy to care for and well-suited for hanging baskets. Its graceful foliage adds a lush, tropical touch to any indoor space.
variants.images.label: Aeschynanthus japhrolepsis

description.en: For bold style, look no further than our Chess pot in striking black, cobalt and brown hues. The checked print is hand stamped to create a grid of artfully imperfect squares, adding a playful twist to a traditionally uniform pattern. The artisanal finish lends each pot a unique look. Pair yours with an equally bold plant for a design contrast, or team with simpler foliage to put the pattern centre stage.

description.en: Mini Succulent Set is a charming collection of small, hardy succulents, each with unique shapes and textures. description.en: Concrete Pot is a sturdy and stylish planter made from durable concrete, perfect for both indoor and outdoor use. description.en: Fiddle-Leaf Fig is a popular indoor plant admired for its large, violin-shaped leaves and bold, sculptural presence. It thrives in bright, indirect light and prefers moderate watering. Easy to care for with the right conditions, it adds a dramatic, stylish touch to any room.

Easy to care for, they thrive in bright light and require very little water. Arriving in nursery pots, they’re perfect for creating a stylish, low-maintenance display with bold vertical accents.

Aloe juvenna, also known as Tiger Tooth Aloe, is a compact succulent with stacked, spiky leaves marked by delicate white spots. Its distinctive appearance adds a sculptural, desert-inspired touch to any collection.

description.en: Nursery pots are lightweight, practical containers used for growing and transporting plants. Made from flexible plastic, they promote healthy root development and provide excellent drainage. They’re designed for function rather than style, making them ideal for propagation, repotting, and temporary housing. Many people place nursery pots inside decorative planters to keep plants neat while still allowing easy watering and care.
variants.images.label: nursery pots green

description.en: Large Succulent Set is a beautifully curated collection of sizable, easy-care succulents with diverse shapes, colors, and textures. Arriving in nursery pots, they’re ready to be arranged in decorative planters for a bold, modern touch of greenery.

description.en: Wild Banana is a lush indoor foliage plant known for its large, tropical leaves that instantly create a vibrant, jungle-like feel. description.en: Epipremnum 'Global Green' is a vibrant trailing indoor plant with glossy, heart-shaped leaves in a rich, uniform green. Perfect for hanging baskets, shelves, or as a climbing plant, it adds lush greenery and a fresh, tropical feel to any space.

description.en: Fibrestone Cube Pot – Dark Gray is a modern, durable planter made from lightweight fibrestone. description.en: Parodia warasii is a charming, globe-shaped cactus known for its bright green body and neat rows of soft, golden spines. variants.images.label: Parodia warasii

description.en: Dischidia oiantha 'Variegata' is a charming trailing plant with thick, variegated leaves that add texture and brightness to any space. description.en: Polaskia chichipe is a striking columnar cactus known for its branching, tree-like shape and dense clusters of short spines. variants.images.label: Rubber Plant
